short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Find, prioritize and fix vulnerabilities in the open source dependencies used to build your cloud native applications

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Prioritize faster and make data-driven security decisions.
This Snyk security browser extension brings the Snyk information and vulnerability insights straight into your browser surfing experience as you view supported package ecosystem websites.
